Lovstakken K(1), Peterson L, Homer AL.

Author information:
(1)Norwegian Police College.

Anabolic steroids are now recognized as a widespread addictive and dangerous 
substance, no longer exclusively used as an aid to muscle size and strength in 
world-class athletes. Psychologists have neglected prevention programs for 
steroid abuse, in part because of a lack of knowledge of the precipitants of 
