Weighing up disability.

James KC(1), Foster SD.

Author information:
(1)Department of International Health, Boston University School of Public 
Health, MA 02118, USA.

Comment in
    Lancet. 1999 Oct 9;354(9186):1306.
    Lancet. 2000 Jun 10;355(9220):2079-80.

Comment on
    Lancet. 1999 Jul 10;354(9173):111-5.

