567. Kidney Int. 1999 Jul;56(1):324-32. doi: 10.1046/j.1523-1755.1999.00540.x.

Long-term outcome of dialysis patients in the United States with coronary 
revascularization procedures.

Herzog CA(1), Ma JZ, Collins AJ.

Author information:
(1)Department of Internal Medicine, Hennepin County Medical Center, University 
